Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it when Princess Celestia\Ncomes to Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my hooves shined\Njust like Rarity for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ya like?\N- I certainly do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised she's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are\NApplejack and Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's detained helping Applejack\Nwith a mishap at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't get why\Nthe Princess would be so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's bringing\Nan important visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor who's important and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's somepony\Nso terribly important,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she still had many more terribly important\Nthings to do before she got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the visitor has a deer antler,\Na goat leg, a bat wing, and a snake tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. That's Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in the\Nwide-wide world of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,would Princess Celestia\Nbring along someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 10\NKeep Calm and Flutter On
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect,\NPrincess Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how could you bring Discord here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware that\Nthe last time Discord was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he created serious havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If by "serious havoc"\Nyou mean
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"turning Ponyville into\Nthe chaos capital of the world".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And tricking us all into being\Nthe opposite of our true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And making yummy delicious\Nchocolate milk rain all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,without a single dollop of whipped cream\Nto go with it anywhere in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single dollop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have use for Discord's magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if it can be reformed\Nto serve good instead of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why\NI've brought Discord here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because I believe you are the ponies\Nwho can help him do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This will never work!\NThis is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How will we control him?!\NWe're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Need I remind you\Nthat you are the ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who turned him back into stone\Nlike this in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we can just use\Nthe Elements of Harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,against him again\Nif he gets out of hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably need a volunteer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to run away from here\Nright away to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll do it!\N- No need, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have them right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've cast a spell so Discord\Ncan't take them and hide them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where is Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she may know best\Nhow to begin reforming Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's he goin' on about now?\N- Good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beaverton Beaverteeth has agreed\Nto take his dam apart and move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My apple trees are so waterlogged\NI can practically hear 'em gargle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But he says first you'll have\Nto apologize for calling him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"a nuisance".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize?!\NHe's lucky I didn't call him a varmint!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beaverton Beaverteeth!\NSuch a language!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know what\NI would've done without ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, slackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Double time it over to Ponyville,\Nwould ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all waiting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that this is a tall order,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't ask\Nif I weren't confident
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you could get him to use magic\Nobediently of his own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really think\NI'll know best how to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I must return to Canterlot\Nfor Equestria's royal summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You may release Discord when ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, ponies,\Nguess it's time to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just hope\Nthis releasing spell works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd best keep our elements on\Nat all times until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time somepony\Ngot me out of that prison block.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, stretching of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're a creature of chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,stone bodysuits aren't\Nyour typical go-to fashion choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make that bunny cute again! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He is adorable the way he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what else is adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You ponies truly believe\Nthat you can reform me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you're putting your faith\Nin this one here to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes me wanna pinch\Nyour little horsey cheeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Being turned to stone doesn't keep me\Nfrom hearing every word Celestia says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I admit\Nit makes rolling my eyes a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, unless you want us\Nto turn you back to stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll zap those animals back\Nthe way they were pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you wouldn't dare\Nturn me back to stone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and risk disappointing\Nyour precious princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Try us, "Dip-cord"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can treat\Npoor defenseless animals like that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and get away with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You go, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd best watch your step, buster,\Nor I'll give you the Stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Stare?\NOh no, please, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything but\Nyour disapproving eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! No no no, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I can't take it any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you say!\NBecause...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it turns out we need to use\Nour elements against you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can convince Princess Celestia\Nit was for a good reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like I know\Nwhere I'll be crashing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,while I'm being "reformed"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With you, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be horrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean\Nwe have to act the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We should at least\Ntry to be hospitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind giving up\Nyour favorite spot on the couch,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,do you, Angel Bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry about Angel.\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Thank you,\NFluttershy, for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If only your pony friends\Ncould be as considerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just trying to drive a wedge\Nbetween us, like he always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now why in the world would\NI ever try to do a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't unite and use the Elements\Nof Harmony against you, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You big liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, look who's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can plainly see\Nthat I'm not big at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There, all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not gonna be easy,\Nbut Princess Celestia's counting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think\NI actually know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the key is to befriend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Being kind to him and letting him\Nbe my house guest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably\Nthe best way to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you really think that'll work?\N- I think it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but if you need us,\Nall you need to do is whisper "help",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll be back here\Nwith our Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So watch that\Ngoat-legged step of yours, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Look at me!\NI'm practically reformed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really alright\Nwith him staying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I think we should\Ncome up with a backup plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in case this whole "befriending"\Nbusiness doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Discord we're talking about,\Ngirls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be a bad idea\Nto have another trick up our sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I know just the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord? Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Discord, I just want\Nto make sure you know that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's anything I can do to--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you eating... paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I? How odd of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just heading out, so,\Nmake yourself at home while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, have a nice time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is fine here, bye bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You like carrots, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing your owner for a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'ya like them carrots?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.\NThe spell I had in mind isn't in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, where are the other books\NI asked you to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to have a\Nreforming spell up and running pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if he makes the\NElements of Harmony disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,like he did last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia cast a spell\Nprotecting them, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia didn't cast a spell\Nprotecting our books!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I thought\NI'd find the reforming spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nthis isn't overdoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You said to make myself at home\Nwhile you were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't want\Nto overstep my bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I did say that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,if this makes you more comfortable,\Nby all means, please feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it does, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so very kind,\Nmy dear Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew that you were\Nthe understanding one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not like those nasty friends of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends aren't nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you'd say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it just goes to show\Nhow understanding you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,\NI think Princess Celestia is right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,when she singles you out\Nas the one who could reform me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're off to such a good start\NI'm seriously considering actually
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,being reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!\NFluttershy, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! I hear Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, what's going on?\NAre you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine, everything's going great.\NIsn't it, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to get you away\Nfrom Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just terrible and,\Nfrom the looks of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,completely out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you're wrong!\NWe're making great progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm earning his trust by giving him\Na little space to be himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate to break it to you,\Nbut he used that "space to be himself"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to tear out all the reforming spells\Nfrom the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That does explain the paper eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He ate them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we aren't gonna need a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already really\Nconsidering being reformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you believed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be his friend,\NI have to start by giving him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the benefit of the doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell you what. Bring all the ponies over\Nfor a dinner party this evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I bet his manners\Nwill have really improved by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even get him to put the cottage\Nback on the ground first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Dinner it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're having\Na dinner party with Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This evening\Nis sure to be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad I didn't bother wearing\Nmy fanciest outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy thinks this is the way\Nto reform Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and asked us\Nto give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, our pony guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so delighted\Nthat you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, do come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See what a beautiful job\Nhe did helping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord set the entire table himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take your...\Nhats, ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on to your elements, girls.\NIt's gonna be a bumpy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all know,\NPrincess Celestia hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd help Discord use his magic\Nfor good, instead of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, care for some gravy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a cute little\Ngravy boat you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you are! Yes you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one creepy little\Ngravy boat if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on now, Dashie,\Nyou're not even giving this a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.\NMistakes happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, everypony,\Ndancing candles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not falling for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's just trying\Nto distract us from--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's another "mistake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think you just made them mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something fishy going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's hardly my fault\Nif the soup tureen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,finds the term "something fishy"\Nto be offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the dress. Not the dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That tureen's only doin'\Nwhat you're makin' it do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's not jump\Nto any conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy,\Ncan't you see what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing innocent with you\Nso you'll never agree to use
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the Elements of Harmony\Nagainst him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a bit harsh,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying,\Nright, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that\NDiscord's far from perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also see none of you\Ngiving him a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep cutting him\Nso much slack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ever remember my house being\Nthis lively before you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, I've...\Nnever really had a friend before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not a good time, Angel.\NWe're having a dinner party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up! I think he's tryin'\Nto tell us somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet Apple Acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Flooding at Sweet Apple Acres!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all know who's\Nbehind that now, don't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of your\N"friend" now, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen\Nthe floodin' this bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They've built dams round here before,\Nbut never like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Such language!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.\NThey won't listen to a word I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Discord's\Nbehind all this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you all think I'm a silly,\Ngullible fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been trying to gain\Nhis friendship any way I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so he'd come to trust\Nand listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Fluttershy, you want a turn?\NThe water's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to see if it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A sight for sore eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, there's a big mess\Ndown here at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Awful business, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Applejack's home,\Nand it's being destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by innocent creatures\Nwho would never be acting this way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if it weren't for\Nyour reckless behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I will fix it.\NI only ask one thing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that you never use\Nyour Element of Harmony against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As a sign of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never use\Nmy Element of Harmony against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There, much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I do prefer ice skating\Nto water skiing! Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fixing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I oughta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong, pal?\N- Don't call me your pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come skating with me,\Nand we'll let bygones be bygones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Fluttershy!\NGame on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He fixes this or\Nhe goes back to being stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia will understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a promise not to use\Nmy element against him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to have fun with me\Nbecause we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't use the elements against me\Nbecause we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not. Your. Friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do whatever I want,\Nwhenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Discord, the master of chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You think\Nyou can boss Discord around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm just going to\Nturn all this back because you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if I don't\NI'll lose the one friend I ever had?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well played, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well played.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked it better my way, but...\NI guess when you're friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't always have things\Nexactly your way all the time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Princess,\NI'm ready to use my magic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for good instead of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your success,\Nponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely sense\Na big change in Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the Elements of Harmony\Nwith you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right\Nwhen you said Fluttershy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the one to find\Nthe way to reform Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By treating Discord as a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,she got him to realize\Nthat friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was actually important to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And something that, once he had,\Nhe didn't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...\NFriendship is magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See?\NHe can be a real sweetheart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,once you get to know him.
